        "old_string": "# CDS Tranche Implementation Progress\n\n## Understanding of Patterns\n\n1. **Product Module**:\n   - CDS/CdsIndex have `@BeanDefinition` with properties decorated with `@PropertyDefinition`\n   - Implements `Product`, `Resolvable<ResolvedXXX>`, `ImmutableBean`, `Serializable`\n   - Trade wrappers (CdsTrade, CdsIndexTrade) implement `ProductTrade`, `ResolvableTrade`, `ImmutableBean`\n   - Resolved forms (ResolvedCds, ResolvedCdsIndex) are immutable beans\n\n2. **Pricer Module**:\n   - IsdaCdsProductPricer has methods like `price()`, `presentValue()`, etc.\n   - Pricers handle ISDA standard calculations\n\n3. **Measure Module**:\n   - TradeCalculationFunctions (e.g., CdsIndexTradeCalculationFunction) implement CalculationFunction<T>\n   - They wire trade types to calculation functions\n\n## Files to Create\n1. CdsTranche.java - product\n2. CdsTrancheTrade.java - product\n3. ResolvedCdsTranche.java - product\n4. ResolvedCdsTrancheTrade.java - product (maybe needed)\n5. IsdaCdsTranchePricer.java - pricer\n6. CdsTrancheTradeCalculationFunction.java - measure\n7. ProductType.java - needs CDS_TRANCHE constant\n\n## Files to Modify\n1. ProductType.java - add CDS_TRANCHE",
